Class IntDataParameter

java.lang.Object
  sim.Parameter
      sim.IntParameter
          sim.IntDataParameter

public class IntDataParameter
extends IntParameter

IntDataParameter is to be used to store a simulation parameter which is dynamic during running of the simulation. It can be displayed in a DataParamPanel by setting its parent DataParamLine using the setParamLine() method.

1 (12/11/2010)
